ingPlugin.cc?at=default#cl-600) in the scoring code.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>We've had a report that in V3, the score did not increment from 3 to 4 after rotating the valve.  A potential cause (not yet confirmed) is that the hose became unscrewed enough (e.g., due to gravity) after getting the 3rd point and before turning the valve.</p>\n<p>This problem can be avoided by relaxing <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"#!/osrf/drcsim/src/826552d800ba1fd84554b7f46f9757249f663565/ros/atlas_msgs/VRCScoringPlugin.cc?at=default#cl-600\" rel=\"nofollow\">the check</a> in the scoring code.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": {"display_name": "Brian Gerkey", "uuid": "{3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:2e35028e-9ad8-4d6a-a3a5-275159a304a9/5fa9ec73-0fec-4860-a202-e34ae23b6a12/128"}}, "nickname": "Brian Gerkey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:2e35028e-9ad8-4d6a-a3a5-275159a304a9"}, "state": "resolved", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2013-06-02T20:09:45.068080+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2013-06-07T15:41:01.871063+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 314}